Enum BdaType

    public enum BdaType
extends java.lang.Enum<BdaType>
    This Enumeration includes all possible Types for IEC 61850 leave nodes ( BasicDataAttribute). This includes BasicTypes and CommonACSITypes as defined in part 7-2.
